                  <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************     -->
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>stele of naiskos type with acroteria at the peak and corners. below the
                           pediment is a flat moulding with the inscription. at the center of the
                           stele, a young female figure that can be identified in Philippe faces
                           frontally, with blank eyes; at her right, a male figure is depicted in
                           high relief, with his head overlying the inscription.</p>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
